                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "kEZOi",
                          "name": "p1",
                          "fill": "#B0B0B0",
                          "content": "1. CLAUDE.md 分層架構 — 全域、專案、模組三層指令檔的組織策略，確保 AI 在不同範圍都能獲得正確的上下文指引。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.7,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "4teYe",
                          "name": "p2",
                          "fill": "#B0B0B0",
                          "content": "2. Sub-task 自動化模式 — 使用 TodoWrite 追蹤多步驟任務，搭配 Task tool 委派子代理執行，大幅提升複雜任務的完成率。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.7,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "sY3I4",
                          "name": "p3",
                          "fill": "#B0B0B0",
                          "content": "3. 漸進式信任策略 — 從保守的權限設定開始，隨著對工具信任度提高逐步開放 allowedTools，避免初期過度授權帶來的風險。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.7,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
