                          "content": "Custom slash commands、MCP server 整合、Git hooks 自動化、多層 CLAUDE.md、Permission 管理等 7 項建議均已在 Workshop 體系中實作。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.7,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
